data.description: Welcome to this exquisite 5-bedroom, 4-bath waterfront home situated in the coveted Hypoluxo Pointe neighborhood.  A boater's delight, this home offers a 55-foot dock complete with a motorized lift ideal for boat enthusiasts.  Recently upgraded, this home features a host of modern additions, including hurricane impact windows, an impressive outdoor kitchen, and a meticulously revitalized pool/spa entertainment area adorned with tumbled marble decking. Fresh exterior paint and artful light scaping further elevate the property's allure. This  residence is conveniently located near the Boynton Beach inlet, offering unhindered access with no fix bridges and dockside dining options at nearby restaurants. Don't miss your chance to own this waterfront boater's haven.
